==See also==
* [[HMS Greatford]] (P3109), a 1950s [[Ford class seaward defence boat]], built for initial training for [[University Royal Naval Unit]]. It was 35 metres long, and was around 120 tonnes with one 40&nbsp;mm and two 20&nbsp;mm anti-aircraft guns.

